1466
01:38:35.996 --> 01:38:38.123
Claro.

1467
01:38:38.957 --> 01:38:40.792
Gaylord Focker,

1468
01:38:42.461 --> 01:38:45.130
aceita ser meu genro?

1469
01:39:07.235 --> 01:39:10.781
Greg? Pensei que
tivesse voltado para Chicago.


1470
01:39:10.947 --> 01:39:13.367
